      "body" : "@MarkSlater forget about 1 and -1 returned from compareTo and use only 0. Then things will be as simple as comparsion operator is between two compared numbers. So value1.compareTo(value2) <i>operator</i> 0 is same as value1 <i>operator</i> value2"
