      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "BigDecimal.compareTo() starts by comparing signums as an optimisation. So it&#39;s probably best to call compareTo(), as it&#39;s more intention-revealing and only costs the price of an extra method call (which I suspect would get inlined anyway)."
